3. cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) - The experimental results of the paper are based on the MNIST dataset, which is a dataset commonly used in computer vision research. 
4. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - The paper discusses deep learning as a service and on-device augmented intelligence, which are topics related to artificial intelligence. 
5. cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) - The paper provides efficient algorithms for dissipating irrelevant uncertainty, which is a topic related to data structures and algorithms.
